ackedCompilationConfiguration.java`\n  - `tests/src/org.jetbrains.kotlin/kotlin-main-kts/2.3.21/src/test/java/org_jetbrains_kotlin/kotlin_main_kts/JavaBackedEvaluationConfiguration.java`\n  - `tests/src/org.jetbrains.kotlin/kotlin-main-kts/2.3.21/src/test/java/org_jetbrains_kotlin/kotlin_main_kts/JavaBackedHostConfiguration.java`\n\nThe new Kotlin test creates a script definition from a `@KotlinScript` template that uses those Java configuration classes. This should force `ConfigurationFromTemplateKt` through the no-arg constructor discovery and instantiation paths for compilation, evaluation, and host configuration via the public `createScriptDefinitionFromTemplate` API.\n\nI did not run tests and did not modify reachability metadata or Native Image config.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0da4d2342ba752470169fa1b86ac24819e8a73a2344ad2e60b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1414, "output": 801, "cacheRead": 79872, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 82087, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777998708484, "responseId": "resp_0da4d2342ba752470169fa1b753d18819eaa54fe4f22dc8019"}, "toolResults": []}
